 output writer is still writable. Contributed by
 Erik Krogen.

(cherry picked from commit 98d9e9c4c823d865ddfc017e71c82d12c8328e53)
(cherry picked from commit c997fc629d9b89ba998decc56d410cf6341a71d9)

